[h2]What is it?[/h2]
It prevents players from accidentally murdering non-hostile Frogg and Shadow NPCs in cold blood.

[h2]Why'd you make it?[/h2]
Because I got tired of my turrets - which I placed to *protect* the innocent Froggs and Shadows - mowing them down instead.  I didn't see any other mods doing this, so I did it myself.

