¯\_(ツ)_/¯

[h2]Is this compatible with other mods?[/h2]
As long as those mods don't depend on the Frogg and Shadow NPC types having a damage team other than "friendly", then yes, this should be fully compatible with them.

[h2]Will this break my saves?[/h2]
Highly unlikely.  It's just two JSON patches.  Uninstalling will simply revert the damage teams to vanilla (returning them to being vulnerable to damage by the player and/or the player's turrets).

